  "body": "At this time, there is no good way to find transactions that were invoked by a smart contract.  There is also no good way to tell which accounts were created by a smart contract.\n\nMaybe when displaying tx data from getBlock or getTransaction, there should be a field called 'invoked by' with a value of the address of the contract-account that invoked that transaction (if that tx was indeed invoked by a contract.)  \n",
