    "body": "still can't find a way to get transactions invoked by a smart contract\n\nfor example: https://etherchain.org/tx/0x0ebd7cb54091a16c5bfeae91af530c36b1f5835d179f30e5612b695b9da66c8e\n\ngeth doesn't recognize this tx:\n\n```\n> eth.getTransaction('0x0ebd7cb54091a16c5bfeae91af530c36b1f5835d179f30e5612b695b9da66c8e')\nnull\n```\n\nthere are 4 transactions in the block: https://etherchain.org/block/1654861\ngeth returns only 3 transactions:\n\n```\n> eth.getBlock(1654861);\n{\n  difficulty: 45869825130269,\n  extraData: \"0x426974436c756220455448204d696e696e6720506f6f6c\",\n  gasLimit: 4712388,\n  gasUsed: 81383,\n  hash: \"0x49be7f625c431e8aed0835219cb2cc10f8511329d59f3a1f6b04fe35c9208043\",\n  logsBloom: \"\",\n  miner: \"0xf3b9d2c81f2b24b0fa0acaaa865b7d9ced5fc2fb\",\n  nonce: \"0xcc50dd3f518e3b06\",\n  number: 1654861,\n  parentHash: \"0x5f3359d233528ce7b37adf3e9a0a918075c492f94d50ca1e34c09964e6f80529\",\n  receiptRoot: \"0x899e6bb902f0078583b0e12581606cc91af611020eb9fb944f1eeffd4eaea0ef\",\n  sha3Uncles: \"0x1dcc4de8dec75d7aab85b567b6ccd41ad312451b948a7413f0a142fd40d49347\",\n  size: 1040,\n  stateRoot: \"0xeef31084bf004d26382c7d38a65db326696cb3a2a74d5c34651ceb8048b10e4f\",\n  timestamp: 1465224882,\n  totalDifficulty: 25190219693809040138,\n  transactions: [\"0x95645eaafb29179ac3d62a9944868b55ef7e63d9eeafecca34d3559407934674\", \"0x0b5636e832f46ba8da882c56fe5b104f23d2d230a30e4037e1a66b5ec7071df0\", \"0x37c76fc1fc9bcfd2ffa857cc874c4fd303a25ebfa10428f378ffcadb2a7a286e\"],\n  transactionsRoot: \"0x7dbd69f9a198536f856809b11343377eb61941ce69b65a18c342efd8e6d02457\",\n  uncles: []\n}\n```\n",
